parameters.name: Sample_UTC
parameters.description:
Universal time of the sample at the spacecraft (UTC, spacecraft event         
                        time). The time appears as 6 integer columns (year, day of year, hour,        
                        minute, second, millisecond). Individual elements of the time column are      
                        separated by a single ASCII space character and have leading zeros            
                        omitted. The individual elements can be read by using the FORTRAN format      
                        '(1X,I4,1X,I3,3(1X,I2),1X,I3)' IYR IDOY IHR IMIN ISEC IMSEC

parameters.name: Decimal Day
parameters.description:
Decimal day of year. This column provides a 
                        second representation of the sample time.

parameters.name: BX Payload
parameters.description: B field X-component in payload coordinate system.

parameters.name: BY Payload
parameters.description: B field Y-component in payload coordinate system.

parameters.name: BZ Payload
parameters.description: B field Z-component in payload coordinate system.

parameters.name: Gain Range Payload
parameters.description:
Gain range of instrument at time of the sample.  Pertains
                        to B components in payload coordinate system.  A negative
                        value indicates a high-resolution (detail word), as versus
                        fullword, entry.

parameters.name: BX Sun State
parameters.description: B field X-component in Sun-state coordinate system.

parameters.name: BY Sun State
parameters.description: B field Y-component in Sun-state coordinate system.

parameters.name: BZ Sun State
parameters.description: B field Z-component in Sun-state coordinate system.

parameters.name: Gain Range Sun State
parameters.description:
Gain range of instrument at time of the sample.  Pertains
                        to B components in Sun-state coordinate system.  A negative
                        value indicates a high-resolution (detail word), as versus
                        fullword, entry.
